{"tid":653794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【留名！恥笑！】美提多項要求！若中方不履行承諾 將升級關稅措施","createTime":"2018-05-05T04:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T06:44:48.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f445762a68c7ba5a274318e6999c3e3532f3fa3f","tid":653794,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》中文網微博引述美國貿易代表團的文件，指美國要求中國立即降低貿易不平衡程度，更提出多項要求，表明若中國未能遵守已達成一致的承諾，則將採取進一步關稅措施。<br />\n<br />\n文件顯示，美方要求中方不要針對美國農民和農產品；不要就美國對來自中國的投資，加以限制進行報復，並於在7月1日前就外國投資發佈負面清單；要求中方將所有商品關稅降至不高於美國的水平；於2020年前，將中美貿易順差縮窄2,000億美元；停止對中國制造2025計劃中涉及的行業進行補貼，並要求與中國每個季度舉行會議以評估進展。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示中國官員認為美方的提議「不公平」。<br />\n<br />\n內地官媒及官方機構陸續發佈消息，商務部新聞發言人表示，在3日至4日舉行的中美經貿磋商中，中方就中興公司案與美方進行了嚴正交涉，而美方則表示重視中方交涉，將向美國總統特朗普報告中方立場；中國外交部則表示中美經貿磋商仍在繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》報道，中美雙方就經貿問題進行了坦誠、高效、富有建設性的討論，雙方均認為發展健康穩定的中美經貿關系對兩國十分重要，致力於通過對話磋商解決有關經貿問題。此外，雙方就擴大美對華出口、雙邊服務貿易、雙向投資、保護知識產權、解決關稅和非關稅措施等問題充分交換了意見，在有些領域達成了一些共識，而雙方認識到，在一些問題上還存在較大分歧，需要繼續加緊工作，取得更多進展，故同意繼續就有關問題保持密切溝通，並建立相應工作機制。"},{"pid":"9ab4035b9e5e476563b3976f697f171155eb8d39","tid":653794,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b44ad5afe7412a2a6b0e5ebacfd454592c7f21","tid":653794,"uid":30169,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/140552_60a3b4804b449821829ccdb87b81a10a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F140552_60a3b4804b449821829ccdb87b81a10a.png&h=3a654062&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8b46d8a753661c4355ecbbb644272af04b44593","tid":653794,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfab59aa27e2c71e9add83fdbb431e15d41cc42f","tid":653794,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"對人公平啲等級對自己不公平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那"},{"pid":"637071edd77ba86dbeb5db43927bc5deb4dfced8","tid":653794,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfab59aa27e2c71e9add83fdbb431e15d41cc42f","tid":653794,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"對人公平啲等級對自己不公平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個一路犯開規既人被要求守規 反而屌人地對佢唔公平<br />\n真係支那先講得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4220c786546e90ff8c81e650b0d8c0ae5349c88","tid":653794,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"科研又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n火燭又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中興又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美興又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵制又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no